  "description": [
    {
      "type": "heading2",
      "content": {
        "text": "What you’ll do",
        "spans": []
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": {
        "text": "In this interactive workshop, work with professional game designers to create your own text-based game on iPads using the web platform Twine. You’ll have the opportunity to learn the basics of game design theory. ",
        "spans": []
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": {
        "text": "By the end of the session, you’ll have created your own short game that you can access at home.",
        "spans": []
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": {
        "text": "All the equipment is provided – you won’t need to bring a thing. We’ll provide snacks, too. ",
        "spans": []
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "heading2",
      "content": {
        "text": "About your facilitators",
        "spans": []
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": {
        "text": "Two games designers from Three Knots games studio will be running the session.",
        "spans": [
          {
            "start": 25,
            "end": 49,
            "type": "hyperlink",
            "data": {
              "preview": {
                "title": "http://threeknots.co.uk/"
              },
              "url": "http://threeknots.co.uk/"
            }
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "heading2",
      "content": {
        "text": "Who can come",
        "spans": []
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": {
        "text": "All young people aged 14–19 are welcome, on your own or in small groups. If you’re arriving with a parent, they can drop you off at the door.",
        "spans": []
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": {
        "text": "If you have any access requirements, please get in touch by email ahead of the session. ",
        "spans": [
          {
            "start": 60,
            "end": 65,
            "type": "hyperlink",
            "data": {
              "preview": {
                "title": "mailto:access@wellcomecollection.org"
              },
              "url": "mailto:access@wellcomecollection.org"
            }
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "heading2",
      "content": {
        "text": "Where we’ll be",
        "spans": []
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": {
        "text": "The Studio is on Level 1. Head upstairs and follow the signs to the Studio. There are 25 places in each workshop and it’s first come, first served. ",
        "spans": []
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": {
        "text": "",
        "spans": []
      }
    }
